layers.nm: We have clients all over the globe --each with their own needs and challenges. And, they trust GDE to deliver professional quality content. But we don't stop at hi-res video and great audio; social impact requires more. We maintain a pulse on current trends, social platforms, cultures, and sensibilities. The Genie Deez team is composed of producers, salespeople, and artists who know how to leverage the contemporary media landscape in order create meaningful impact. 2
